ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I highly recommend the class. You will not only have to write lab reports and learn to analyse flame data, but also get a chance to lecture to the rest of the class about a topic. This involves doing research into that topic and also helps with teaching skills and cultivating them. A rewarding class where I learnt a good deal.
If you use laser for combustion study, you cannot miss it.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course helped a lot and deepen the understanding of the discipline, which is going to be fundamental for the remaining of the program.
Absolutely a help....definitely useful for research.
